title: Strength Arborae
content:
Strength Arborae is a potion made using the Alchemist profession which increases the strength of each Arborae attack.


 * +40 Potion Strength Arborae
 * +50 Potion Strength Arborae
 * +60 Potent Potion Strength Arborae
 * +70 Potion Strength Arborae
 * +80 Potent Potion Strength Arborae
